QuestData.Title: Return to MacKinley
QuestData.Description: Here, take this pouch and give it to Sea Wolf. And tell him I meant to pay him back! I swear!!$B$BI just got a little drunk and lost my way, and...you know how things are. He'll understand - you don't have to get rough!
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Shaky's Payment to "Sea Wolf" MacKinley.
QuestData.CompletionText: Here here, $n. Did you get Shaky's payment?
QuestData.RewardText: Heh heh, well done! And when you showed Shaky those giblets, how hard did he shake?$B$BHah! He's so easy to read, when I play cards with him I can't help but win!$B$BThanks for your help, $n. Now it's your turn to get paid...
